<p>Designer Cam Wilde assembled this <a href="https://www.behance.net/gallery/193759/Periodic-Table-of-Typefaces">&#8220;periodic table of typefaces&#8221;</a> by tabulating each face&#8217;s representation among a selected honor roll of great typefaces.</p>
<p>The &#8220;elements&#8221; are sorted numerically, and each is categorized as to family and class: sans-serif, serif, script, blackletter, glyphic, display, grotesque, realist, didone, garalde, geometric, humanist, slab-serif, and mixed. (Click to enlarge.)</p>
